                    <physDesc>
                        <objectDesc>
                            <supportDesc>
                                <support><p>A quadrangular base of off-white limestone, with a moulding running around all four sides of the bottom edge (now lost on the left side). The upper part of the base is lost. All four sides are smoothly finished, and the front side preserves a Greek inscription of at least 6 lines.</p>
                                    <material key="limestone" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/66.html">limestone</material>
                                    <objectType key="altar" ref="http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/30.html">altar
                                    <certainty locus="value" match="../@key" assertedValue="base"><desc>base</desc></certainty></objectType>
                                    <dimensions>
